OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fbright end to the day then a dry night
OL,7,Fwith long clear spells throughout.
OL,8,FBecoming chilly overnight in some
OL,9,Fsheltered valleys.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FAnother dry day with long
OL,12,Fperiods of sunshine. Becoming rather
OL,13,Fwarm inland by the afternoon but
OL,14,Fcooler near the east coast.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FHigh
OL,17,Fpressure will maintain the dry and
OL,18,Fsettled weather with sunshine at
OL,19,Ftimes. Feeling quite warm inland but
OL,20,Fcooler along coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
